    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a really harsh way to put it. but i guess it's true. i look at the numbers every night, the rent, the groceries, the interest... and i realize that if i weren't here, that money could actually go toward their future instead of just keeping us afloat for one more month of misery. it feels like a math problem i can't solve.",
